# Excluded from Docker build context. The dashboard Dockerfile uses
# `context: ../..` (the repo root) — Docker reads `.dockerignore` from
# the context root, NOT from the Dockerfile's directory, so this file
# (rather than `packages/dashboard/.dockerignore`) is what governs.
#
# Critical: exclude `**/node_modules`. The host's node_modules carries
# Windows-flavoured pnpm `.bin/` shims that don't resolve when copied
# into a Linux container — we want the container's pnpm install to
# generate Linux-correct shims, untouched.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/coverage
**/dist
**/build
**/*.log
**/.turbo
.git
.gitignore
.env
.env.*
packages/dashboard/.env
